      "img": "systems/n5eb/icons/svg/items/feature.svg",
      "system": {
        "description": {
          "value": "<p>The Spirit Companion is usually incorporeal unless it is willed otherwise.</p><p> While Physical Manifestation is not active, they cannot interact with or be interacted with by the physical world, cannot be seen by creatures without chakra sight or true sight, have a 30 foot flying speed and can hover, can pass through up to 5 feet of obstruction and the spaces of other creatures as if they were not there.</p><p> If they end your turn in an occupied space, they are shunted to the nearest unoccupied space.</p><p></p>",
          "chat": ""
        },
