          "value": "<p>While Physical Manifestation is active, you can choose to have a jutsu that you or your Spirit Companion casts originate from either of your spaces.</p><p> Additionally, if you or your Spiritual Companion would cast a jutsu that makes at least one attack roll or forces at least one saving throw, you both become eligible to target a creature that was hit or failed their saving throw with a jutsu with the Finisher keyword regardless of range, once per turn, as an Action, Bonus Action, or Reaction, ignoring its listed casting time.</p><p> You may still only cast one jutsu as a Finisher per turn.</p><p></p>",
